<li id="cite_note-221"><b><a href="#cite_ref-221" title="">^</a></b> The legislation specifically excluded the territories of the <a href="/wiki/Honourable_East_India_Company" title="Honourable East India Company" class="mw-redirect">Honourable East India Company</a> which were not then under direct Crown control.</li>
